<section class="viewHeader" , style="top: 100px;">
	<div class="jumbotron">
		<div class="title">
			<h4>WELLBEING OF LGBT COMMUNITIES</h4>
			<p>Compared with the general population, LGBT people are more likely to face crime. General Social Survey 2020 (GSS 2020)  suggested around 8% of participants with non-mainstream sexual orientations have experienced assault or break-in in the last 12 months, which is 2 times of that for heterosexuals</p>
			<p>This survey also found this community also tend to have lower trust in the healthcare system, the police, and the justice system. </p>
				<p>Switch between Heterosexual and Homosexual community to view the level of trust</p>
			<button class="button button-secondary button-pipaluk" id="ht">Heterosexual group</button>
			<button class="button button-secondary button-pipaluk" id="hm">Homosexual group</button>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

